[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿A tube station in London has a problem.",
        "startTime": 1745,
        "endTime": 5873,
        "slowStartTime": 2767,
        "slowEndTime": 9035
    },
    {
        "text": "Each month, 15 people are injured on its escalators.",
        "startTime": 8757,
        "endTime": 12159,
        "slowStartTime": 13286,
        "slowEndTime": 18464
    },
    {
        "text": "But a surprising solution for the station has emerged.",
        "startTime": 12975,
        "endTime": 15877,
        "slowStartTime": 19612,
        "slowEndTime": 24040
    },
    {
        "text": "Wait for it.",
        "startTime": 16877,
        "endTime": 17551,
        "slowStartTime": 25465,
        "slowEndTime": 26552
    },
    {
        "text": "Hello everybody and please listen up.",
        "startTime": 18547,
        "endTime": 20207,
        "slowStartTime": 27971,
        "slowEndTime": 30535
    },
    {
        "text": "I said to my colleague that my wife was bringing down the two kids...",
        "startTime": 20351,
        "endTime": 23525,
        "slowStartTime": 30676,
        "slowEndTime": 35513
    },
    {
        "text": "...to meet me after work.",
        "startTime": 23599,
        "endTime": 24611,
        "slowStartTime": 35549,
        "slowEndTime": 37141
    },
    {
        "text": "Take care on the escalator, hold on to the handrail and your luggage.",
        "startTime": 24856,
        "endTime": 28425,
        "slowStartTime": 37434,
        "slowEndTime": 42863
    },
    {
        "text": "And he said, \"Would Megan mind doing a PA announcement...",
        "startTime": 29653,
        "endTime": 32827,
        "slowStartTime": 44629,
        "slowEndTime": 49466
    },
    {
        "text": "...regarding the safety on the escalators?\"",
        "startTime": 32921,
        "endTime": 35121,
        "slowStartTime": 49531,
        "slowEndTime": 52906
    },
    {
        "text": "She does like a bit of acting so I knew she'd be up for it.",
        "startTime": 35399,
        "endTime": 38179,
        "slowStartTime": 53248,
        "slowEndTime": 57493
    },
    {
        "text": "It took several takes to get the perfect recording.",
        "startTime": 40677,
        "endTime": 43300,
        "slowStartTime": 61166,
        "slowEndTime": 65175
    },
    {
        "text": "I was really nervous when I was first going to do it...",
        "startTime": 44007,
        "endTime": 46823,
        "slowStartTime": 66160,
        "slowEndTime": 70460
    },
    {
        "text": "...but then once I did it, I thought, \"This is actually okay.\"",
        "startTime": 46916,
        "endTime": 50072,
        "slowStartTime": 70524,
        "slowEndTime": 75333
    },
    {
        "text": "Research shows that deeper adult voices...",
        "startTime": 51349,
        "endTime": 54385,
        "slowStartTime": 77174,
        "slowEndTime": 81803
    },
    {
        "text": "...are perceived by humans as having more authority.",
        "startTime": 54487,
        "endTime": 56925,
        "slowStartTime": 81880,
        "slowEndTime": 85613
    },
    {
        "text": "Take care on the escalator, hold on to the handrail and your luggage.",
        "startTime": 57115,
        "endTime": 60625,
        "slowStartTime": 85823,
        "slowEndTime": 91162
    },
    {
        "text": "A child's voice wouldn't have that authority...",
        "startTime": 61246,
        "endTime": 63613,
        "slowStartTime": 92019,
        "slowEndTime": 95645
    },
    {
        "text": "..but perhaps it's the shock factor.",
        "startTime": 64039,
        "endTime": 66551,
        "slowStartTime": 96208,
        "slowEndTime": 100051
    },
    {
        "text": "Megan's announcements have been running at the station for 6 months.",
        "startTime": 67143,
        "endTime": 70333,
        "slowStartTime": 100865,
        "slowEndTime": 105724
    },
    {
        "text": "Transport for London says injuries have fallen by almost two thirds.",
        "startTime": 70965,
        "endTime": 74831,
        "slowStartTime": 106598,
        "slowEndTime": 112472
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you think adults listen enough to children?",
        "startTime": 75939,
        "endTime": 78179,
        "slowStartTime": 114058,
        "slowEndTime": 117493
    },
    {
        "text": "No.",
        "startTime": 79569,
        "endTime": 80104,
        "slowStartTime": 119504,
        "slowEndTime": 120381
    },
    {
        "text": "They should listen more to children...",
        "startTime": 80657,
        "endTime": 82573,
        "slowStartTime": 121136,
        "slowEndTime": 124084
    },
    {
        "text": "...because sometimes children are right.",
        "startTime": 82647,
        "endTime": 84889,
        "slowStartTime": 124121,
        "slowEndTime": 127558
    }
]